    <entry>
      <title>网易云音乐命令版</title>
      <link href="/posts/NeteaseTermux/"/>
      <url>/posts/NeteaseTermux/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="tip "><p>仓库链接<br><a class="ghcard" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/darknessomi/musicbox"><img src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/pin/?username=darknessomi&repo=musicbox&show_owner=true"/></a></p></div><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><p>1.安装python（如果有安装就不用安装了）<div class="tip warning"><p>安装过程会提示 Do you want to continue?[Y/n]，输入y即可</p></div></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg i python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.安装mpg123声音插件（必装插件）<div class="tip warning"><p>安装过程会提示 Do you want to continue?[Y/n]，输入y即可</p></div></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg i mpg123</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.安装网易云命令版（NetEase-MusicBox）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install NetEase-MusicBox</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">musicbox</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/Netease/mmexport1627006247163.5vhg6vo8r3k0.jpg"></p><p>5.卸载</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip uninstall NetEase-MusicBox</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6.更新</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>教程完成</p><div class="tip "><p>作者链接</p></div><a class="ghcard" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/max27149"><img src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/?username=max27149&show_owner=true"/></a> <h2 id="功能特性"><a href="#功能特性" class="headerlink" title="功能特性"></a>功能特性</h2><ol><li>320kbps 的高品质音乐</li><li>歌曲，艺术家，专辑检索</li><li>网易 22 个歌曲排行榜</li><li>网易新碟推荐</li><li>网易精选歌单</li><li>网易主播电台</li><li>私人歌单，每日推荐</li><li>随心打碟</li><li>本地收藏，随时加 ❤</li><li>播放进度及播放模式显示</li><li>现在播放及桌面歌词显示</li><li>歌曲评论显示</li><li>一键进入歌曲专辑</li><li>定时退出</li><li>Vimer 式快捷键让操作丝般顺滑</li><li>可使用数字快捷键</li><li>可使用自定义全局快捷键</li><li>对当前歌单列表进行本地模糊搜索</li></ol><h3 id="键盘快捷键"><a href="#键盘快捷键" class="headerlink" title="键盘快捷键"></a>键盘快捷键</h3><p>有 num + 字样的快捷键可以用数字修饰，按键顺序为先输入数字再键入被修饰的键，即 num + 后的快捷键。</p><table><thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Effect</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><kbd>j</kbd></td><td>Down</td><td>下移</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>k</kbd></td><td>Up</td><td>上移</td></tr><tr><td>num + <kbd>j</kbd></td><td>Quick Jump</td><td>快速向后跳转 n 首</td></tr><tr><td>num + <kbd>k</kbd></td><td>Quick Up</td><td>快速向前跳转 n 首</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>h</kbd></td><td>Back</td><td>后退</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>l</kbd></td><td>Forword</td><td>前进</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>u</kbd></td><td>Prev Page</td><td>上一页</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>d</kbd></td><td>Next Page</td><td>下一页</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>f</kbd></td><td>Search</td><td>当前列表模糊搜索</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>[</kbd></td><td>Prev Song</td><td>上一曲</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>]</kbd></td><td>Next Song</td><td>下一曲</td></tr><tr><td>num + <kbd>[</kbd></td><td>Quick Prev Song</td><td>快速前 n 首</td></tr><tr><td>num + <kbd>]</kbd></td><td>Quick Next Song</td><td>快速后 n 首</td></tr><tr><td>num + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>g</kbd></td><td>Index for Song</td><td>跳到第 n 首</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>=</kbd></td><td>Volume +</td><td>音量增加</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>-</kbd></td><td>Volume -</td><td>音量减少</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>Space</kbd></td><td>Play/Pause</td><td>播放/暂停</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>?</kbd></td><td>Shuffle</td><td>手气不错</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>m</kbd></td><td>Menu</td><td>主菜单</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>p</kbd></td><td>Present/History</td><td>当前/历史播放列表</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>i</kbd></td><td>Music Info</td><td>当前音乐信息</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>p</kbd></td><td>Playing Mode</td><td>播放模式切换</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>a</kbd></td><td>Add</td><td>添加曲目到打碟</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>a</kbd></td><td>Enter Album</td><td>进入专辑</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>g</kbd></td><td>To the First</td><td>跳至首项</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>g</kbd></td><td>To the End</td><td>跳至尾项</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>z</kbd></td><td>DJ List</td><td>打碟列表</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>s</kbd></td><td>Star</td><td>添加到收藏</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>c</kbd></td><td>Collection</td><td>收藏列表</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>r</kbd></td><td>Remove</td><td>删除当前条目</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>j</kbd></td><td>Move Down</td><td>向下移动当前项目</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>k</kbd></td><td>Move Up</td><td>向上移动当前项目</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>c</kbd></td><td>Cache</td><td>缓存歌曲到本地</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>,</kbd></td><td>Like</td><td>喜爱</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>.</kbd></td><td>Trash FM</td><td>删除 FM</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>/</kbd></td><td>Next FM</td><td>下一 FM</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>q</kbd></td><td>Quit</td><td>退出</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>t</kbd></td><td>Timing Exit</td><td>定时退出</td></tr><tr><td><kbd>w</kbd></td><td>Quit &amp; Clear</td><td>退出并清除用户信息</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>使用Android手机搭建Hexo</title>
      <link href="/posts/phonehexo/"/>
      <url>/posts/phonehexo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-安装Termux"><a href="#1-安装Termux" class="headerlink" title="1,安装Termux"></a>1,安装Termux</h1><div class="tip "><p>1.你可以通过F-Droid下载<br><a class="btn-beautify button--animated orange larger" href="https://f-droid.org/packages/com.termux/"   title="F-Droid下载地址"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>F-Droid下载地址</span></a></p></div><h1 id="2-给储存权限，切换清华大学源"><a href="#2-给储存权限，切换清华大学源" class="headerlink" title="2, 给储存权限，切换清华大学源"></a>2, 给储存权限，切换清华大学源</h1><p>1.给储存权限,</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">termux-setup-storage</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/mmexport1627006271057.4tliy6618is0.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/mmexport1627006260218.5p8upyc1ki80.jpg"></p><p>2.给完权限后切换清华大学源</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sed -i <span class="string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*stable main\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/termux-packages-24 stable main@&#x27;</span> <span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sed -i <span class="string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*games stable\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/game-packages-24 games stable@&#x27;</span> <span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/game.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sed -i <span class="string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*science stable\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/science-packages-24 science stable@&#x27;</span> <span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/science.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tip warning"><p>3.更新过程会提示Do you want to continue?[Y/n]，输入y即可</p></div><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/mmexport1627006256090.7fh0a9grfz00.jpg"></p><h1 id="3-安装nodejs和git"><a href="#3-安装nodejs和git" class="headerlink" title="3, 安装nodejs和git"></a>3, 安装nodejs和git</h1><div class="tip warning"><p>1.安装过程会提示Do you want to continue?[Y/n]</p></div><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install nodejs-lts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>切换镜像源</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> registry http://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/mmexport1627006256090.7fh0a9grfz00.jpg"><br>输入y即可</p><p>2.和上面一样要输入y</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="4，初始化Hexo并安装Hexo"><a href="#4，初始化Hexo并安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="4，初始化Hexo并安装Hexo"></a>4，初始化Hexo并安装Hexo</h1><p>1.可能需要几分钟</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.初始化hexo并创建blog文件夹，安装速度取决于你的网络和设备读写速度。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.切换到blog</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.安装Hexo</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6.开启本地预览</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tip "><p>访问地址: http:localhost:4000</p></div><p>如果主页图显示正常，那就恭喜你已经成功安装Hexo了<br>最后放上一张成功的截图<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/hexo.p6ko1ibqwg0.jpg"></p><h1 id="5，-复制博客文件夹到内置储存（方便后续美化修改）"><a href="#5，-复制博客文件夹到内置储存（方便后续美化修改）" class="headerlink" title="5， 复制博客文件夹到内置储存（方便后续美化修改）"></a>5， 复制博客文件夹到内置储存（方便后续美化修改）</h1><p>1.返回到主目录</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后复制blog文件夹到sdcard/blog</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mv blog /sdcard（这是把blog目录移动到内部储存）</span><br><span class="line">这是分割线。。。。。。。</span><br><span class="line">cp -rf blog /sdcard（这是把blog目录复制到内部储存）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.复制完成后的截图<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6blog.152gb55yots0.jpg"></p><p>打开Mt管理器<br>你会看到一个blog文件夹</p><p>下次用可以直接使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /sdcard</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/mmexport1627006251621.2khkqwvzc6e0.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Karune-SHI-E/image@master/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/hexo.p6ko1ibqwg0.jpg"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Hexo教程 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Hexo </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>hexo源码备份到github仓库</title>
      <link href="/posts/hexoBackup/"/>
      <url>/posts/hexoBackup/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>git备份hexo常用命令</p><h3 id="初始化git版本库"><a href="#初始化git版本库" class="headerlink" title="初始化git版本库"></a>初始化git版本库</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="重命名github分支"><a href="#重命名github分支" class="headerlink" title="重命名github分支"></a>重命名github分支</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch -m master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="GitHub远程仓库关联"><a href="#GitHub远程仓库关联" class="headerlink" title="GitHub远程仓库关联"></a>GitHub远程仓库关联</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote add origin git@github:用户名/仓库名.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="添加文件到本地库"><a href="#添加文件到本地库" class="headerlink" title="添加文件到本地库"></a>添加文件到本地库</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地源码更新"><a href="#本地源码更新" class="headerlink" title="本地源码更新"></a>本地源码更新</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;update&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地提交到Github"><a href="#本地提交到Github" class="headerlink" title="本地提交到Github"></a>本地提交到Github</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="从本地强制更新到Github仓库"><a href="#从本地强制更新到Github仓库" class="headerlink" title="从本地强制更新到Github仓库"></a>从本地强制更新到Github仓库</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push origin -f master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Hexo教程 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
